column16: Jose Bautista grounds out, third baseman Logan Forsythe to first baseman Allan Dykstra.
Josh Donaldson doubles (3) on a line drive to center fielder Mikie Mahtook.   Steve Tolleson scores.
Devon Travis homers (2) on a fly ball to left field.
Dalton Pompey flies out to right fielder Steven Souza Jr.
Kevin Pillar pops out to first baseman Logan Forsythe in foul territory.
Justin Smoak singles on a line drive to center fielder Kevin Kiermaier.   Josh Donaldson scores.    Jose Bautista scores.
Dioner Navarro pops out to first baseman Logan Forsythe in foul territory.
Dee Gordon singles on a ground ball to right fielder Brandon Guyer.   Martin Prado to 2nd.
Martin Prado singles on a line drive to right fielder Brandon Guyer.
Christian Yelich strikes out on a foul tip.
Dee Gordon ground bunts into a force out, catcher Rene Rivera to shortstop Asdrubal Cabrera.   Donovan Solano out at 2nd.    Dee Gordon to 1st.
Chris Davis flies out to center fielder Desmond Jennings.
Orioles challenged (tag play), call on the field was overturned: Travis Snider doubles (1) on a line drive to right fielder Steven Souza Jr.   Steve Pearce scores.
